description: Retrieves a list of active sessions for a Dev Environment in a project.

parameters.name: projectName
parameters.description: The name of the project in the space.

parameters.name: devEnvironmentId
parameters.description: The system-generated unique ID of the Dev Environment.

nested_items.name: items
nested_items.description: Information about each session retrieved in the list.

nested_items.name: projectName
nested_items.description: The name of the project in the space.

nested_items.name: devEnvironmentId
nested_items.description: The system-generated unique ID of the Dev Environment.

nested_items.name: startedTime
nested_items.description: The date and time the session started, in coordinated universal time (UTC) timestamp format as specified in RFC 3339

nested_items.name: id
nested_items.description: The system-generated unique ID of the Dev Environment session.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: A token returned from a call to this API to indicate the next batch of results to return, if any.
